channel.title: mycatalog updates
channel.description: 'My Catalog' uses the IBM Cloud catalog API to retrieve data from the catalog. It attempts to be as accurate as possible. This feed shows additions, updates, removals from the catalog. Use with care. It is a work-in-progress :)

item.title: [updated] ProtectIO DRaaS DIY (primaryio-protectio) has a new plan named primaryio-protectio-protectio-100-revised
item.description: ProtectIO 100 plan is used to protect maximum up to 100 virtual machines. Once number of protected virtual machines reaches maximum limit, customer will be automatically upgraded to next tier.

item.title: [updated] ProtectIO DRaaS DIY (primaryio-protectio) has a new plan named primaryio-protectio-protectio-enterprise-revised
item.description: ProtectIO Enterprise plan is used to protect any number of virtual machines above 1001. This plan has no limitations on number of protected virtual machines.
